  <brief_title>Safety, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of BMS-936559 in Severe Sepsis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1b/2a, Randomized, Double-Blinded, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of BMS-936559 in Subjects With Severe Sepsis</official_title>
