  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Part 1: Safety of BMS-936559 in subjects with severe sepsis - measured by the incidence rates of death, AEs, SAEs, AEs leading to discontinuation, AEs of special interest and laboratory abnormalities</measure>
    <time_frame>Approximately 3 months</time_frame>
    <description>Safety will be measured by the incidence rates of death, Adverse event (AEs), Serious adverse event (SAEs), AEs leading to discontinuation, AEs of special interest (identified from PD-L1 oncology trial), and laboratory abnormalities</description>
  </primary_outcome>
